{"tid":1034163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急!! 被人襲擊，尋找車牌TT2843車主","createTime":"2019-02-23T16:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T17:01:02.000Z","uid":65979,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"998e5111565fa663ab27b72ee651b638a300aa34","tid":1034163,"uid":65979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"(借朋友AC 開post)<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我喺星期五晚(2/22) 晚上9點30分左右比另一半帶到一個僻靜地方掌摑，持續左20-30分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n我冇反抗，係因為我地係同我家人同住。我怕逃走/反抗嘅話會激起佢進一步對我家人不利。我懦弱，我抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n嗰度入夜之後冇途人，亦唔見有巡警。但係我留意到當時有部車(車牌TT2843)泊左喺度，希望車cam 影到事發經過，等我可以訴諸法律保護自己。如果唔係就算我搵社工/報警，最多都只會不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n而家我本身已經長期比另一半家暴。為防對方發現我出post 而報復，我只好將事發地點加密。如果車主有保留相關片段，希望可以聯絡我，tg: siuleemotherflyknife<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23809289a8f2a8ba7f16911dcbe3b84717f56c7d","tid":1034163,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ae5ac4181d31bece9b746f8357c98cd390f86a7","tid":1034163,"uid":65979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23809289a8f2a8ba7f16911dcbe3b84717f56c7d","tid":1034163,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:43:34.000Z","msg":"你試下九點幾十點上去，隨街打飛機都冇人見到"},{"pid":"2e2bfe711204683258be88aa168d34aa108362af","tid":1034163,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082c64a1360bd16679b99882ae572db90ad7f9b7","tid":1034163,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b6ef04f822c03044213f54ab9776ae229202fc","tid":1034163,"uid":201604,"li